WEBVTT

00:00:13.430 --> 00:00:14.290
Please come in.

00:00:20.510 --> 00:00:21.440
Grand Tutor, this is who

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:25.100
You've been meaning to meet, the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

00:00:28.120 --> 00:00:31.760
Your Majesty has finally shown your true face.

00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:35.840
I have no choice.

00:00:38.070 --> 00:00:40.400
Young Lord Xiao has seen right through me.

00:00:40.560 --> 00:00:41.760
Any more concealment

00:00:42.280 --> 00:00:43.540
Would be meaningless.

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:45.670
Your Majesty feels unwell,

00:00:45.670 --> 00:00:48.520
Yet you are still personally hosting the peace talks.

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:49.880
It is never easy to be a mother.

00:00:49.880 --> 00:00:51.390
My end is drawing near.

00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:55.860
I have to settle certain matters myself before my passing.

00:00:56.470 --> 00:00:57.670
This trip of mine is

00:00:58.710 --> 00:00:59.750
Partly

00:01:00.240 --> 00:01:01.640
For an old acquantaince,

00:01:02.150 --> 00:01:03.350
And partly

00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:05.870
For you, Grand Tutor Xie.

00:01:13.070 --> 00:01:15.350
Haven't you always been wondering

00:01:17.120 --> 00:01:20.070
About the truth of the gruesome case where the An and Lu families

00:01:20.070 --> 00:01:23.070
Colluded with the enemy and allied with the Northern Qin's

00:01:23.070 --> 00:01:24.200
Right King of Virtue

00:01:24.310 --> 00:01:27.840
From the Mulian family to establish their own administration?

00:01:29.760 --> 00:01:31.960
I had not yet entered the palace by then.

00:01:32.039 --> 00:01:34.300
Some things are not easy to investigate.

00:01:34.590 --> 00:01:35.509
That said, I am

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:39.220
Willing to cooperate with you, Grand Tutor Xie.

00:01:39.280 --> 00:01:41.070
Didn't Your Majesty just say

00:01:41.509 --> 00:01:43.430
That your end is drawing near?

00:01:43.759 --> 00:01:45.160
Do you think cooperation

00:01:45.560 --> 00:01:47.160
Is impossible when I am dead?

00:01:50.759 --> 00:01:51.950
It is not true.

00:01:52.950 --> 00:01:54.039
Only when I am dead

00:01:54.430 --> 00:01:55.890
Can the two of us cooperate

00:01:56.870 --> 00:01:58.560
On some issues.

00:03:33.360 --> 00:03:36.940
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

00:03:37.110 --> 00:03:39.870
[Episode 12]

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:44.670
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

00:03:46.120 --> 00:03:47.630
Don't be so petty.

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:49.650
I know this workshop belongs to Yuan Xiaoliu.

00:03:49.650 --> 00:03:51.380
I'm just borrowing it for a bit.

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:52.460
Frankly speaking,

00:03:52.470 --> 00:03:53.870
This looks quite like the one at my home.

00:03:53.870 --> 00:03:56.150
Don't all workshops look similar?

00:03:56.960 --> 00:03:57.710
Wait, who told you

00:03:57.710 --> 00:03:58.750
This was meant for Yuan Xiaoliu?

00:03:58.750 --> 00:04:00.280
So this is not his workshop?

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:02.810
How could he charge me rent?

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:08.760
Explain this.

00:04:09.590 --> 00:04:10.680
It's about a private job I took

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:11.870
At the Miraculous Craft shop.

00:04:11.870 --> 00:04:13.470
The well in Honglu Temple was clogged,

00:04:13.470 --> 00:04:14.600
So I went to clear it.

00:04:18.800 --> 00:04:19.510
What about this?

00:04:19.510 --> 00:04:21.000
This is for cracking sunflower seeds.

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:22.600
Look, just turn it like this,

00:04:23.070 --> 00:04:24.930
And a load of seeds can be cracked.

00:04:27.240 --> 00:04:28.870
This copper ball here contains fragrances.

00:04:28.870 --> 00:04:30.560
Didn't you say the people of Northern Qin eat strong-smelling food,

00:04:30.560 --> 00:04:31.430
And thus have noticeable body odors?

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.430
If they carry this around,

00:04:32.430 --> 00:04:33.630
Their odors can be covered,

00:04:33.630 --> 00:04:35.680
And the pleasant scent in it will last for several months.

00:04:35.680 --> 00:04:38.159
Did you still plan to blow up the Eagle King with fire thunderstones?

00:04:38.159 --> 00:04:39.090
Definitely not.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:40.830
I...

00:04:42.159 --> 00:04:43.720
Who said I went see him?

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:44.450
That's a lie.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:45.930
Keep lying then.

00:04:46.600 --> 00:04:48.070
Didn't you go to meet the Eagle King

00:04:48.070 --> 00:04:49.130
For Li Lejun today?

00:04:50.190 --> 00:04:52.730
Tell me. What did you promise to give the Eagle King in exchange

00:04:52.730 --> 00:04:54.790
For halting the political marriage?

00:04:55.310 --> 00:04:55.950
Spill it.

00:04:57.930 --> 00:04:59.190
Repeating crossbows?

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:00.920
Gunpowder?

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:17.800
Xie Jiayu,

00:05:18.560 --> 00:05:19.690
Tell me what this is.

00:05:20.160 --> 00:05:20.870
Don't hit me in the face!

00:05:20.870 --> 00:05:22.070
This is refined iron.

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:24.180
And this is your so-called solution?

00:05:24.560 --> 00:05:26.620
Do you even know this will have you...

00:05:27.660 --> 00:05:28.720
You're such a fool.

00:05:31.270 --> 00:05:33.720
I didn't trade the iron casting technique to the Eagle King.

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:34.980
Please say something!

00:05:35.040 --> 00:05:36.680
I really didn't betray Ye.

00:05:36.870 --> 00:05:38.510
I know sometimes I can be a bit unreliable,

00:05:38.510 --> 00:05:40.570
But I'd never cross the line, would I?

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:43.800
Fine. Believe what you want.

00:05:43.800 --> 00:05:44.480
Alright?

00:05:44.630 --> 00:05:45.820
The Eagle King agreed to set Lejun free

00:05:45.820 --> 00:05:47.430
If I offered the iron casting technique.

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:48.690
Are you satisfied now?

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.630
What exactly are you mad about?

00:05:52.630 --> 00:05:53.120
I already told you

00:05:53.120 --> 00:05:54.480
I didn't sell out the iron casting technique.

00:05:54.480 --> 00:05:56.680
I was merely selling devices of my own creation.

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:58.010
What do you mean by this?

00:05:58.170 --> 00:06:01.310
Your Highness, have you ever heard about the Miraculous Craft?

00:06:01.310 --> 00:06:02.160
No, never.

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:05.870
This Brilliant Manual on Farm Tools records

00:06:06.190 --> 00:06:07.520
All the farm implements

00:06:07.560 --> 00:06:10.310
Designed and improved by the Miraculous Craft, namely me.

00:06:10.310 --> 00:06:12.560
Please look at this foot-treadled water diversion tool.

00:06:12.560 --> 00:06:14.310
By replacing the straight shaft with a curved one

00:06:14.310 --> 00:06:15.510
And adding three fans,

00:06:15.510 --> 00:06:17.070
It can be used to easily reclaim a hundred mu

00:06:17.070 --> 00:06:18.430
Of alkaline earth as farmland a day

00:06:18.430 --> 00:06:20.430
Even in the northern desert region.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.310
And this dragon-bone water-lifting device

00:06:25.310 --> 00:06:27.190
Combines the wisdom of the chapter on waterways in the Record of Trades.

00:06:27.190 --> 00:06:28.680
It saves much manpower.

00:06:28.680 --> 00:06:30.800
With it, even an 80-year-old woman

00:06:30.800 --> 00:06:32.680
Can clear over 70 mu of wasteland.

00:06:33.430 --> 00:06:35.240
Here's a bird-shaped bronze rain gauge.

00:06:35.240 --> 00:06:36.750
The beak is filled with saltpeter,

00:06:36.750 --> 00:06:38.159
While the tail is inlaid with a compass.

00:06:38.159 --> 00:06:39.720
Blue smoke is guaranteed to appear

00:06:39.720 --> 00:06:41.580
Three days before an earthquake.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:47.290
Sweet sorghum can be planted in the southern desert area,

00:06:47.290 --> 00:06:49.190
And cold-region mulberry trees on Mount Yin,

00:06:49.190 --> 00:06:51.510
With the help of iron-rimmed wooden ploughing wheels.

00:06:51.510 --> 00:06:55.390
This page instructs on how to turn saline-alkali land into fertile fields.

00:06:55.390 --> 00:06:58.790
Can Your Highness bear to watch the manual burned into ashes?

00:06:59.900 --> 00:07:00.340
You!

00:07:01.480 --> 00:07:01.920
You...

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:04.450
Don't worry. I've memorized all the content.

00:07:05.950 --> 00:07:07.720
Although Northern Qin has occupied the Capital,

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:10.150
Your people are good at nomadism, not farming.

00:07:10.150 --> 00:07:12.190
Last year, 30,000 head cattle and sheep died from the cold.

00:07:12.190 --> 00:07:14.020
The harvest in the fields were poor.

00:07:14.020 --> 00:07:15.870
The national treasury had few grain reserves.

00:07:15.870 --> 00:07:17.160
The people of Northern Qin

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:18.890
Endured quite a bitter winter.

00:07:19.800 --> 00:07:20.480
But now,

00:07:20.950 --> 00:07:23.010
I can help you break the constraints.

00:07:23.070 --> 00:07:25.670
As long as you call off the marriage to Li Lejun,

00:07:26.390 --> 00:07:28.430
I'll gift you all the instruments

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:30.760
In the Brilliant Manual on Farm Tools.

00:07:30.760 --> 00:07:31.760
What do you think?

00:07:34.630 --> 00:07:35.690
Are all of these...

00:07:36.800 --> 00:07:38.310
Really your inventions?

00:07:39.720 --> 00:07:41.920
Yes, I am exactly the Miraculous Craft.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:46.600
I understand

00:07:46.680 --> 00:07:47.310
That the superior quality

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:49.050
Of Beifu Army's weaponry is based on the iron casting technique.

00:07:49.050 --> 00:07:49.830
I simply used it a pretext

00:07:49.830 --> 00:07:51.960
To lure the Eagle King into meeting me.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.300
Xiao Wuyi, listen.

00:07:55.430 --> 00:07:56.240
I swear,

00:07:56.430 --> 00:07:58.190
If I had truly traded the smelting technique for refined iron

00:07:58.190 --> 00:07:59.120
To the Eagle King,

00:07:59.120 --> 00:07:59.920
Fate would have it

00:07:59.920 --> 00:08:00.950
That I get trafficked again when I leave Jiankang

00:08:00.950 --> 00:08:02.040
-and... -Do you need a fix

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:03.300
On that mouth of yours?

00:08:03.510 --> 00:08:05.510
Can't you stop saying unlucky things?

00:08:05.510 --> 00:08:06.430
I was just trying

00:08:06.430 --> 00:08:07.960
To express my loyalty to Ye.

00:08:08.310 --> 00:08:10.240
You have no idea what I'm mad about.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:12.120
Tell me then.

00:08:12.270 --> 00:08:13.270
You shouldn't have shown your abilities

00:08:13.270 --> 00:08:14.730
In front of the Eagle King.

00:08:15.390 --> 00:08:17.310
Techniques are dead, but people are alive.

00:08:17.310 --> 00:08:18.240
Have you ever considered

00:08:18.240 --> 00:08:19.190
What will happen

00:08:19.190 --> 00:08:20.630
If the Eagle King targets you?

00:08:20.630 --> 00:08:22.270
Aren't you planning to explore the world?

00:08:22.270 --> 00:08:23.560
When I get to the Northern Border,

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:24.480
I'll be too far away to help you.

00:08:24.480 --> 00:08:25.510
Should there be slight negligence

00:08:25.510 --> 00:08:27.070
Or even just an opportunity,

00:08:27.070 --> 00:08:29.120
He can capture you and take you to Northern Qin.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:30.950
Then you won't have anyone to turn to.

00:08:30.950 --> 00:08:32.789
You're not exactly the brave type.

00:08:32.789 --> 00:08:34.120
When your life is in the palm of his hand,

00:08:34.120 --> 00:08:36.450
Will you ever refuse to do what he asks you?

00:08:40.669 --> 00:08:42.480
Well, Mao's always there for me.

00:08:42.789 --> 00:08:44.120
He can protect me too.

00:08:51.230 --> 00:08:51.750
Indeed,

00:08:52.870 --> 00:08:54.670
There is someone to protect you.

00:08:55.240 --> 00:08:57.240
I shouldn't have worried about you.

00:09:25.350 --> 00:09:27.230
The first thing you need is a lesson

00:09:27.230 --> 00:09:28.830
On how to intimidate others.

00:09:29.270 --> 00:09:30.130
In this regard,

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:32.680
Xiao Wuyi has set a good example for you.

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:36.330
Whether to stay or leave

00:09:37.390 --> 00:09:38.240
Is up to you.

00:09:44.040 --> 00:09:45.370
Take good care of Lejun.

00:09:50.610 --> 00:09:53.200
[Cui Mansion]

00:09:55.850 --> 00:09:57.910
[Cui Xi, butler of the Cui Mansion]

00:09:56.630 --> 00:09:58.870
Greetings, Your Highness.

00:10:02.670 --> 00:10:03.800
Just bury this woman

00:10:04.000 --> 00:10:06.800
Who thought she was Princess Qi somewhere random.

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.630
I request a audience with Master Cui.

00:10:10.630 --> 00:10:12.500
No need to enter the premises, Your Highness.

00:10:12.500 --> 00:10:13.690
Master Cui will not

00:10:14.830 --> 00:10:15.960
Meet Your Highness.

00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:19.130
Get out of my way.

00:10:21.390 --> 00:10:24.000
Would you take a look at this, Your Highness?

00:10:24.440 --> 00:10:26.170
Master Cui knew perfectly well

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:28.480
That Your Highness would surely pay a visit

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:31.510
For the political marriage arranged for Princess Pingning.

00:10:31.510 --> 00:10:34.640
So, he insisted that I pass on a message to Your Highness,

00:10:35.080 --> 00:10:38.340
Hoping that you would put the national interests above all

00:10:38.560 --> 00:10:40.420
And prioritize the greater good.

00:10:42.390 --> 00:10:43.520
I must see Master Cui

00:10:43.750 --> 00:10:45.280
For an urgent matter today.

00:10:45.550 --> 00:10:47.350
Please do lend me a helping hand.

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:54.200
Your Highness, have some self-respect!

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:56.550
Do you even know this is the Cui Mansion?

00:10:57.060 --> 00:10:58.520
Is Your Highness trying to

00:10:58.670 --> 00:11:01.930
Ruin the Cui family's good reputation by offering bribes?

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:06.240
I do address you as Your Highness,

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:09.230
But do you really think you're some precious Prince Qi?

00:11:09.230 --> 00:11:10.990
Even Qizhou is long gone—

00:11:11.870 --> 00:11:16.120
Princess Qi was no better than a stray dog, was she?

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:18.320
Mother!

00:11:17.600 --> 00:11:19.540
[Young Li Lejun] [Young Li Mao]

00:11:18.790 --> 00:11:20.550
Mother...

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:22.410
What did you say?

00:11:22.670 --> 00:11:23.120
I said...

00:11:23.120 --> 00:11:23.750
Answer me!

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:27.160
What did you just say?

00:11:29.930 --> 00:11:31.530
Well, actually, I didn't...

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:35.870
I am the Regent now.

00:11:35.870 --> 00:11:37.270
Step forward, I dare you!

00:11:39.150 --> 00:11:40.270
Years ago, Empress Wenxi

00:11:40.270 --> 00:11:41.800
Was incomparably capable.

00:11:42.120 --> 00:11:45.840
She single-handedly helped the nobles migrate to the south safely.

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:47.640
How come the nowadays Cui family

00:11:48.390 --> 00:11:50.550
Is filled with selfish and cowardly gits

00:11:50.550 --> 00:11:52.030
Terrified of death?

00:11:59.440 --> 00:12:00.900
A dignified royal pincess

00:12:01.230 --> 00:12:03.760
Was given away to the rebels by the Cui family.

00:12:12.560 --> 00:12:13.260
Stop!

00:12:14.670 --> 00:12:16.200
It was a misunderstanding.

00:12:20.220 --> 00:12:21.480
What's wrong with you?

00:12:22.410 --> 00:12:25.070
This is Prince Qi, the current Regent.

00:12:22.610 --> 00:12:24.840
[Chief Clerk Cui, master of the Cui family]

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:27.450
How dare you disrespect His Highness?

00:12:27.550 --> 00:12:28.750
Have you completely forgotten

00:12:28.750 --> 00:12:30.480
The etiquette observed by the Cui family?

00:12:30.480 --> 00:12:31.550
-I -Go away!

00:12:31.550 --> 00:12:32.200
Yes.

00:12:36.750 --> 00:12:38.080
Your Highness is paying

00:12:38.910 --> 00:12:43.310
This visit for the political marriage arranged for Princess Pingning, right?

00:12:47.030 --> 00:12:50.440
I know Your Highness can't bear to see the princess marry far away.

00:12:50.440 --> 00:12:53.500
But this political marriage is a major matter of state.

00:12:56.120 --> 00:12:58.720
The Cui family alone cannot interfere with it.

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:03.630
Do you mean the Cui family won't help me?

00:13:04.720 --> 00:13:06.450
It's not that we refuse to help.

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:09.560
It's just that we're unable to render any help.

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:10.860
Your Highness,

00:13:11.390 --> 00:13:13.960
Letting Princess Pingning get married for political purposes

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:15.080
Could actually be

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:17.120
A good thing for you.

00:13:22.790 --> 00:13:24.650
Was Cangfeng Forge built for you?

00:13:24.690 --> 00:13:25.560
Are you in charge now?

00:13:25.560 --> 00:13:26.010
No...

00:13:26.080 --> 00:13:27.360
Did anyone say you could lend it to Xie Jiayu?

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:28.360
You even charged her rent.

00:13:28.360 --> 00:13:29.030
What now?

00:13:30.150 --> 00:13:31.670
Kicking me to the curb after using me, huh?

00:13:31.670 --> 00:13:34.390
Let me ask you. Who exerted his utmost effort

00:13:34.390 --> 00:13:35.240
And racked his brains

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:37.100
To help you keep that girl around?

00:13:37.320 --> 00:13:39.150
So you taught Xie Jiayu how to smelt for refined iron.

00:13:39.150 --> 00:13:40.600
Did I tell you to do that?

00:13:42.240 --> 00:13:43.120
She made it.

00:13:43.390 --> 00:13:44.200
So soon?

00:13:44.790 --> 00:13:45.720
How very gifted.

00:13:46.270 --> 00:13:47.400
She's a rare genius.

00:13:47.630 --> 00:13:49.120
Xiao Wuyi, listen.

00:13:49.390 --> 00:13:51.320
You must do whatever it takes to...

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:56.150
This is not entirely my fault.

00:13:57.440 --> 00:13:59.240
I simply gave her a rough idea.

00:14:00.480 --> 00:14:01.340
Your Highness.

00:14:01.910 --> 00:14:03.770
Prince Qi went to the Cui Mansion.

00:14:04.110 --> 00:14:05.370
What is he doing there?

00:14:05.830 --> 00:14:08.750
[Cui Mansion]

00:14:28.390 --> 00:14:29.120
How did it go?

00:14:30.440 --> 00:14:32.470
Did Chief Clerk Cui say yes?

00:14:43.510 --> 00:14:44.310
Let's go home.

00:14:45.030 --> 00:14:45.600
Master,

00:14:47.080 --> 00:14:48.680
I'd like to take a walk alone.

00:14:56.670 --> 00:14:57.930
Protect His Highness.

00:14:58.010 --> 00:14:58.770
-Yes. -Yes.

00:15:03.680 --> 00:15:04.740
Hurry, over there!

00:15:05.120 --> 00:15:06.600
We'd better not be late.

00:15:07.150 --> 00:15:08.550
This is truly a noble good deed.

00:15:08.550 --> 00:15:11.390
Princess Pingning is marrying into Northern Qin to safeguard Ye.

00:15:11.390 --> 00:15:13.120
The imperial court plans to build a monument for her.

00:15:13.120 --> 00:15:14.270
I'll lead the fundraising!

00:15:14.270 --> 00:15:14.960
I'm going with you!

00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:16.030
- Let's go! - Let's go!

00:15:16.030 --> 00:15:17.560
-Let's all go! -Count me in!

00:15:18.690 --> 00:15:19.550
Hurry up!

00:15:19.550 --> 00:15:21.000
-This is my share. -Come, guys!

00:15:21.000 --> 00:15:22.080
And this is my share.

00:15:22.080 --> 00:15:22.720
Count me in!

00:15:22.720 --> 00:15:23.600
This is my share.

00:15:23.080 --> 00:15:25.550
[Raising funds to repay the princess for protecting Ye]

00:15:23.870 --> 00:15:24.720
This is my share!

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:26.720
Take it all. I'm offering this much.

00:15:26.790 --> 00:15:27.920
And here is my share.

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:28.790
Count me in!

00:15:28.910 --> 00:15:29.870
Smash this place.

00:15:29.870 --> 00:15:30.870
We're also here to contribute.

00:15:30.870 --> 00:15:32.150
No pushing, please!

00:15:32.150 --> 00:15:33.080
This is my share.

00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:35.000
I said, smash this place!

00:15:37.720 --> 00:15:38.390
Go away!

00:15:40.240 --> 00:15:41.440
No donation allowed!

00:15:42.600 --> 00:15:43.270
Scram!

00:15:45.000 --> 00:15:47.270
Grandma!

00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:49.840
Grandma...

00:16:07.630 --> 00:16:10.090
It was who ordered them to break up the crowd.

00:16:13.870 --> 00:16:14.480
Yizhi,

00:16:15.720 --> 00:16:17.240
You shouldn't do things like that.

00:16:17.240 --> 00:16:18.440
Then what should I do?

00:16:22.390 --> 00:16:23.870
You hit a man in the Cui Mansion?

00:16:23.870 --> 00:16:24.320
Yes.

00:16:26.510 --> 00:16:28.110
But I didn't feel pain at all.

00:16:28.360 --> 00:16:29.790
It actually gave me a thrill.

00:16:29.790 --> 00:16:32.190
I should have beaten him to death years ago.

00:16:37.000 --> 00:16:38.600
When a man carries no weapon,

00:16:39.150 --> 00:16:41.210
He can only fight with his bare hands.

00:16:41.480 --> 00:16:42.870
That said, I'm also aware

00:16:42.870 --> 00:16:44.000
There is only one way

00:16:45.030 --> 00:16:46.830
To persuade the noble families.

00:16:48.250 --> 00:16:49.910
Let's bond through marriage.

00:16:49.960 --> 00:16:51.290
Lingyi of the Cui family

00:16:51.600 --> 00:16:52.600
Is a noble lady.

00:16:53.750 --> 00:16:55.240
Having grown up as a bright child,

00:16:55.240 --> 00:16:56.640
She is elegant in manners

00:16:58.030 --> 00:17:00.630
And refined in both appearance and character.

00:17:02.270 --> 00:17:04.329
I swear to resort to any means to unite

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:05.920
All the major noble families

00:17:05.920 --> 00:17:08.170
To fight for a chance to get Your Highness and Princess Pingning

00:17:08.170 --> 00:17:09.589
Out of the current quagmire.

00:17:09.589 --> 00:17:11.160
From this day onward, we the Cui family

00:17:11.160 --> 00:17:13.690
Pledge to stand together with Your Highness.

00:17:14.109 --> 00:17:15.569
Were there dangers ahead,

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:18.280
We would not hesitate to aid Your Highness.

00:17:23.030 --> 00:17:24.550
That day before the palace gate,

00:17:24.550 --> 00:17:26.430
I misspoke in a moment of desperation.

00:17:26.430 --> 00:17:28.270
I know you have your own difficulties.

00:17:28.270 --> 00:17:29.920
But since I am the Regent now,

00:17:30.150 --> 00:17:31.830
I shouldn't rely on you to help my own sister

00:17:31.830 --> 00:17:32.880
Out of trouble.

00:17:34.640 --> 00:17:36.040
I will use my own strength

00:17:36.360 --> 00:17:38.290
To protect those I want to protect.

00:17:38.310 --> 00:17:41.040
I will also continue to promote reforms with you.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:42.590
Then what about Xie Jiayu?

00:17:42.590 --> 00:17:44.190
I'll leave the choice to her.

00:17:46.000 --> 00:17:47.660
With Yaoyao's devotion to me,

00:17:47.860 --> 00:17:49.440
I'm sure she will stick around.

00:17:49.440 --> 00:17:50.790
But you just proposed to marry Ms. Cui.

00:17:50.790 --> 00:17:51.510
So what?

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:55.750
Wuyi, when you asked for Yaoyao's hand in marriage,

00:17:55.750 --> 00:17:57.480
Didn't you already have a wife?

00:17:57.790 --> 00:17:59.510
We both had to adopt expedients, right?

00:17:59.510 --> 00:18:01.440
How could you compare your situation with mine?

00:18:01.440 --> 00:18:03.440
Xie Jiayu and I used to be strangers.

00:18:03.510 --> 00:18:04.840
What's the difference?

00:18:04.880 --> 00:18:05.830
I asked to marry Ms. Cui

00:18:05.830 --> 00:18:07.430
Only to save Lejun, didn't I?

00:18:07.510 --> 00:18:08.440
Yaoyao loves me.

00:18:08.510 --> 00:18:10.240
She will surely understand me.

00:18:10.870 --> 00:18:11.740
Li Yizhi,

00:18:13.160 --> 00:18:15.220
You're even a worse bastard than I am.

00:18:18.480 --> 00:18:19.280
You're right.

00:18:20.880 --> 00:18:21.920
If being a good person

00:18:21.920 --> 00:18:23.880
Only turns me into a pawn,

00:18:28.200 --> 00:18:29.790
I'd rather be a villain.

00:19:15.750 --> 00:19:16.720
Someone said

00:19:16.880 --> 00:19:18.110
She'd like to forge

00:19:18.110 --> 00:19:19.840
An unparalleled sword for you.

00:19:20.110 --> 00:19:21.750
It must be extraordinarily sharp

00:19:21.750 --> 00:19:23.880
And can be used as a saber.

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:26.790
It also has to be a hundred times better

00:19:26.790 --> 00:19:28.110
Than the Eagle King's Longque Blade.

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:31.310
So, she asked me to teach her how to smelt for refined iron.

00:19:31.310 --> 00:19:34.590
I just didn't know how to decline her request.

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:38.580
What took you so long to say it?

00:19:44.380 --> 00:19:45.440
Where is Xie Jiayu?

00:19:45.880 --> 00:19:47.240
Since the Young Lady's departure earlier today,

00:19:47.240 --> 00:19:49.900
She has not returned to Wensheng Courtyard yet.

00:20:03.160 --> 00:20:03.820
This is bad.

00:20:22.270 --> 00:20:23.590
Are you literally crying

00:20:23.590 --> 00:20:25.030
Because I scolded you a bit?

00:20:25.030 --> 00:20:26.350
You almost exposed my military secrets,

00:20:26.350 --> 00:20:28.550
And I haven't held you accountable yet.

00:20:35.890 --> 00:20:38.690
Did you... temper with my portrait of a noble lady?

00:20:39.300 --> 00:20:40.020
You...

00:20:40.810 --> 00:20:42.070
As the dignified general of Beifu

00:20:42.070 --> 00:20:43.550
And the Heir of Prince Jing'an,

00:20:43.550 --> 00:20:45.810
You appear to keep a distance from women,

00:20:45.920 --> 00:20:48.000
But you're in fact stashing a portrait of a noble lady.

00:20:48.000 --> 00:20:49.200
You have no scruples.

00:20:52.490 --> 00:20:53.310
How is it any of your business?

00:20:53.310 --> 00:20:54.770
I am condemning you for...

00:20:56.050 --> 00:20:57.570
For your future darling.

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.660
If there really is such a girl,

00:21:03.240 --> 00:21:04.440
Let her do it herself.

00:21:14.350 --> 00:21:14.960
Hold on.

00:21:17.550 --> 00:21:18.750
Swords and blades are used by people.

00:21:18.750 --> 00:21:19.830
Shouldn't the length and form

00:21:19.830 --> 00:21:20.790
Be designed based on

00:21:20.790 --> 00:21:22.650
The user's height and arm length?

00:21:23.110 --> 00:21:24.240
Look at this sloppy draft.

00:21:24.240 --> 00:21:25.510
Did you even put your heart into it?

00:21:25.510 --> 00:21:26.910
Why are you so demanding?

00:21:28.640 --> 00:21:30.680
Is this how the Miraculous Craft does business?

00:21:30.680 --> 00:21:31.740
You're receiving a gift.

00:21:31.740 --> 00:21:32.720
Why so picky?

00:21:32.880 --> 00:21:34.030
This is just how I am.

00:21:34.400 --> 00:21:36.270
I only accept gifts that are to my liking.

00:21:36.270 --> 00:21:37.800
If not, don't give any to me.

00:21:39.270 --> 00:21:40.400
Reach out your arms.

00:21:42.620 --> 00:21:44.420
I don't have a tape measure here.

00:21:59.710 --> 00:22:02.440
♪ One glance from near stirs my heart ♪

00:22:02.660 --> 00:22:05.210
♪ This fleeting moment ♪

00:22:06.910 --> 00:22:10.920
♪ Tugs the threads woven by fate ♪

00:22:11.090 --> 00:22:13.090
♪ Bound tight evermore ♪

00:22:15.050 --> 00:22:18.050
♪ Sharing all the years together ♪

00:22:18.460 --> 00:22:22.830
♪ Peace I find nowhere but by your side ♪

00:22:23.420 --> 00:22:26.330
♪ Bear witness with our souls ♪

00:22:26.400 --> 00:22:28.920
Your hairband surely has many uses.

00:22:27.260 --> 00:22:30.720
♪ Fear no partings or wax and wane ♪

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:29.720
Yes.

00:22:30.200 --> 00:22:31.110
It kills, too.

00:22:37.240 --> 00:22:38.750
If you don't want to be taken by the Eagle King

00:22:38.750 --> 00:22:40.480
To Northern Qin for hard labor,

00:22:40.890 --> 00:22:42.070
Then don't slack off anymore during your practice

00:22:42.070 --> 00:22:43.930
Of lightness skills with Yan Yue.

00:22:44.400 --> 00:22:47.530
At least, they can help you escape when you get in danger.

00:22:47.720 --> 00:22:48.920
Thanks to these skills,

00:22:48.920 --> 00:22:50.270
You'll be able to go anywhere alone

00:22:50.270 --> 00:22:51.330
In this vast world.

00:22:59.440 --> 00:23:00.640
The visiting delegation

00:23:00.640 --> 00:23:02.920
Includes the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

00:23:02.920 --> 00:23:04.720
She and the Eagle King are after different benefits.

00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:06.880
It's easier to halt the political marriage through her.

00:23:06.880 --> 00:23:08.350
But before the peace talks complete,

00:23:08.350 --> 00:23:10.070
And the Eagle King leaves Jiankang,

00:23:10.070 --> 00:23:11.870
You'd better stay away from him.

00:23:12.430 --> 00:23:13.290
Did you hear me?

00:23:14.160 --> 00:23:15.090
Yes, I heard you.

00:23:15.500 --> 00:23:17.700
You're so nagging, just like my mother.

00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:23.810
I want to see Mao.

00:23:29.070 --> 00:23:29.730
No problem.

00:23:31.310 --> 00:23:32.570
I'll tell him about it.

00:23:56.790 --> 00:23:57.550
My Lady, isn't Mount Ya

00:23:57.550 --> 00:23:58.960
The place that Prince Qi yearns

00:23:58.960 --> 00:24:00.020
To go with you most?

00:24:00.110 --> 00:24:01.310
Why is it crossed out?

00:24:05.510 --> 00:24:06.510
Mao probably

00:24:07.790 --> 00:24:09.160
Won't go there with me.

00:24:09.750 --> 00:24:11.830
My Lady, don't be upset.

00:24:12.590 --> 00:24:14.000
I'll always be with you.

00:24:16.880 --> 00:24:19.680
I think I'm feeling something other than sadness.

00:24:20.070 --> 00:24:23.200
Do you remember that trip along the river with lanterns?

00:24:24.070 --> 00:24:26.640
We wrote our wishes on small paper boats at that time.

00:24:26.640 --> 00:24:28.110
I took a peek at Mao's.

00:24:28.400 --> 00:24:29.350
He wrote

00:24:30.070 --> 00:24:33.200
That he hoped Lejun and Yaoyao's wishes would come true.

00:24:34.110 --> 00:24:36.440
Prince Qi has always been a nice gentleman

00:24:36.640 --> 00:24:39.440
Who cares deeply about you and Princess Pingning.

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:40.850
But he seems to never

00:24:41.070 --> 00:24:43.130
Really have anything he truly wants.

00:24:43.640 --> 00:24:44.590
I decided to run away from marriage,

00:24:44.590 --> 00:24:45.720
And he went with me.

00:24:46.310 --> 00:24:48.030
Even though he has become the Regent,

00:24:48.030 --> 00:24:50.560
He's ready to leave with me as long as I want to.

00:24:52.160 --> 00:24:54.090
But it seems I've never figured out

00:24:54.160 --> 00:24:56.020
What Mao truly wants for himself.

00:24:56.350 --> 00:24:57.150
My Lady,

00:24:57.920 --> 00:24:59.850
What do you want for yourself then?

00:25:19.110 --> 00:25:20.920
Xiao Wuyi treats you really well.

00:25:20.920 --> 00:25:22.240
You're not related to him or anything,

00:25:22.240 --> 00:25:23.350
Yet he especially built a workshop

00:25:23.350 --> 00:25:24.810
For you in his own mansion.

00:25:27.200 --> 00:25:28.350
It's midnight. Why did you

00:25:28.350 --> 00:25:30.070
Come here instead of sleeping?

00:25:30.070 --> 00:25:30.870
I can't sleep.

00:25:31.350 --> 00:25:33.750
Hearing the sounds here can soothe my mind.

00:25:43.240 --> 00:25:44.550
This is a military secret.

00:25:44.550 --> 00:25:47.030
You want to see it? Ask me to be your master first.

00:25:47.030 --> 00:25:48.110
As if I care.

00:25:48.440 --> 00:25:49.700
I can make that myself.

00:26:10.400 --> 00:26:11.860
Those are blue fireworks.

00:26:13.270 --> 00:26:15.590
Yuan Xiaoliu, I can't believe you know how to make blue fireworks.

00:26:15.590 --> 00:26:17.250
I've never seen these before.

00:26:17.480 --> 00:26:19.470
The books only say that seashells make red fireworks,

00:26:19.470 --> 00:26:20.720
Refined salt, yellow,

00:26:20.720 --> 00:26:21.790
Silver powder, white,

00:26:21.790 --> 00:26:22.960
And azurite, green.

00:26:23.000 --> 00:26:24.260
But blue fireworks...

00:26:25.070 --> 00:26:27.110
Yuan Xiaoliu, you are amazing.

00:26:27.830 --> 00:26:29.440
How come I never noticed it before?

00:26:29.440 --> 00:26:30.200
Blue fireworks

00:26:30.200 --> 00:26:32.060
Were a plaything in my childhood.

00:26:32.170 --> 00:26:33.680
It is also the first type of fireworks

00:26:33.680 --> 00:26:34.880
I've ever made in my life.

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:36.030
How do I compare to you?

00:26:36.030 --> 00:26:37.160
You're impressive.

00:26:37.270 --> 00:26:38.720
But I just won't ask you to be my master.

00:26:38.720 --> 00:26:40.050
What can you do about it?

00:27:00.510 --> 00:27:02.160
Why not use the lightness skills I taught you?

00:27:02.160 --> 00:27:03.550
Add two more sandbags to the training,

00:27:03.550 --> 00:27:04.700
And practice for four more hours tomorrow.

00:27:04.700 --> 00:27:05.560
Did you hear me?

00:27:06.880 --> 00:27:07.720
Yes, I got it.

00:27:07.830 --> 00:27:09.430
I won't be like this anymore.

00:27:10.510 --> 00:27:11.200
Take this.

00:27:23.640 --> 00:27:24.970
His Majesty is too soft,

00:27:25.160 --> 00:27:26.570
And shouldn't have agreed

00:27:26.570 --> 00:27:28.970
To grant Xiao Wuyi any time to reform Beifu.

00:27:48.680 --> 00:27:51.480
I know you've never approved of these peace talks.

00:27:51.590 --> 00:27:53.920
But if you hadn't underestimated the enemy

00:27:53.920 --> 00:27:55.920
And lost a battle at Jiuzhang Plain,

00:27:55.960 --> 00:27:57.110
These peace talks

00:27:57.830 --> 00:27:59.680
Would probably be avoided.

00:28:03.720 --> 00:28:05.590
Given that the emperor is too young,

00:28:05.590 --> 00:28:07.110
And you're holding much military power,

00:28:07.110 --> 00:28:08.510
I demand you to promise me

00:28:08.640 --> 00:28:10.170
That even after my passing,

00:28:10.470 --> 00:28:13.000
You will still be of one mind with the emperor.

00:28:15.270 --> 00:28:16.130
Yes, I promise.

00:28:25.420 --> 00:28:27.940
He really is hiding in Jiankang.

00:28:30.610 --> 00:28:31.410
Your Majesty.

00:28:33.680 --> 00:28:35.540
Where were the fireworks set off?

00:28:35.920 --> 00:28:36.830
Your Majesty,

00:28:37.120 --> 00:28:40.250
The fireworks were set off in Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

00:28:43.520 --> 00:28:45.170
Xiao Wuyi...

00:28:49.200 --> 00:28:51.370
[Honglu Temple]

00:28:52.350 --> 00:28:53.540
I thought Your Majesty

00:28:53.540 --> 00:28:55.070
Would never take my advice.

00:28:56.250 --> 00:28:58.140
I will, provided that you agree

00:28:58.590 --> 00:28:59.880
To find someone for me.

00:29:00.640 --> 00:29:01.240
Who is it?

00:29:01.550 --> 00:29:03.920
I saw a burst of blue fireworks last night.

00:29:04.110 --> 00:29:06.830
That must be the work of an old acquaintance of mine.

00:29:06.830 --> 00:29:07.960
Those fireworks...

00:29:08.200 --> 00:29:10.530
Were set off in Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

00:29:13.400 --> 00:29:14.660
Made by Mulian Ying...

00:29:16.520 --> 00:29:18.850
The very last survivor of the Mulian clan.

00:29:19.900 --> 00:29:21.900
I've spent 20 years looking for him.

00:29:22.270 --> 00:29:25.680
Little did I expect him to be in your hands, Young Lord Xiao.

00:29:27.160 --> 00:29:28.200
Mulian Ying...

00:29:30.640 --> 00:29:32.280
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

00:29:36.640 --> 00:29:38.370
How did you come up with the idea

00:29:39.720 --> 00:29:41.780
Of triggering the fuse with mercury?

00:29:43.480 --> 00:29:45.140
And you fancy being my master.

00:29:45.830 --> 00:29:47.000
Your fireworks suddenly exploded

00:29:47.000 --> 00:29:48.260
And almost injured me.

00:29:49.070 --> 00:29:51.730
Mercury is light in weight and stable in nature.

00:29:52.200 --> 00:29:54.440
It won't kindle fire no matter how you shake it.

00:29:54.440 --> 00:29:56.970
Besides, once the mechanism is activated...

00:29:57.240 --> 00:29:57.960
Look.

00:30:00.440 --> 00:30:01.030
How is it?

00:30:01.030 --> 00:30:02.090
Ignited, isn't it?

00:30:04.550 --> 00:30:05.480
What's with you?

00:30:08.750 --> 00:30:09.440
Nothing.

00:30:10.000 --> 00:30:10.730
Impressive.

00:30:11.400 --> 00:30:13.440
You're way more talented than I am.

00:30:13.880 --> 00:30:14.740
You will surely

00:30:16.590 --> 00:30:18.520
Become a legendary master one day.

00:30:19.920 --> 00:30:20.960
I am so flattered.

00:30:24.180 --> 00:30:26.240
You must take me as your master.

00:30:26.710 --> 00:30:27.710
If necessary,

00:30:27.730 --> 00:30:29.190
I can take you as my master.

00:30:29.270 --> 00:30:30.330
Then, the two of us,

00:30:30.400 --> 00:30:32.000
A duo of master and disciple,

00:30:32.270 --> 00:30:33.440
Will work together to make

00:30:33.440 --> 00:30:35.440
An unparalleled caltrop fireball.

00:30:35.830 --> 00:30:37.070
In my mind right now,

00:30:37.440 --> 00:30:39.480
I'm already picturing us,

00:30:40.070 --> 00:30:42.550
As master and disciple, leaving our mark in history.

00:30:42.550 --> 00:30:44.750
Come on, why is this act again?

00:30:44.920 --> 00:30:45.590
I helped you

00:30:45.590 --> 00:30:46.310
Simply to honor

00:30:46.310 --> 00:30:47.640
My promise to Xiao Wuyi.

00:30:48.890 --> 00:30:50.720
He told me the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

00:30:50.720 --> 00:30:52.720
Saw the blue fireworks we set off that night

00:30:52.720 --> 00:30:53.830
And liked them a lot.

00:30:53.830 --> 00:30:55.310
So she asked Xiao Wuyi to give her some

00:30:55.310 --> 00:30:56.910
To take back to Northern Qin.

00:30:58.880 --> 00:31:00.240
How could I let such an important gift

00:31:00.240 --> 00:31:02.240
For the peace talks easily explode?

00:31:06.400 --> 00:31:09.530
You just mentioned the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin?

00:31:12.400 --> 00:31:13.260
Do you know her?

00:31:14.370 --> 00:31:15.090
Me?

00:31:16.350 --> 00:31:19.810
How could I possibly know the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin?

00:31:20.160 --> 00:31:21.070
I mean,

00:31:21.070 --> 00:31:22.930
She holds such an exalted status.

00:31:23.830 --> 00:31:25.110
What brings her to this place?

00:31:25.110 --> 00:31:28.240
It's said that she's looking for a man named Mulian Ying.

00:31:28.400 --> 00:31:29.960
Recently, Xiao Wuyi has also sent Qing Long and Yan Yue

00:31:29.960 --> 00:31:31.220
To search for this man.

00:31:31.880 --> 00:31:33.340
When this person is found,

00:31:34.030 --> 00:31:36.830
The marriage arranged for Lejun can be called off.

00:31:38.270 --> 00:31:40.810
Xiao Wuyi doesn't even know who Mulian Ying is.

00:31:40.810 --> 00:31:42.470
How is he supposed to find him?

00:31:43.510 --> 00:31:46.110
I heard that he was given a portrait of this man.

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:48.690
It is how the man looked as a teenager, though.

00:32:23.270 --> 00:32:26.310
The draft for the caltrop fireball is beneath the stack.

00:32:26.310 --> 00:32:27.030
Oh, thanks.

00:32:28.480 --> 00:32:29.680
You were not fainted?

00:32:38.220 --> 00:32:39.480
You really are the man,

00:32:40.240 --> 00:32:41.070
Mulian Ying.

00:32:47.790 --> 00:32:51.190
The Empress Dowager of Northern Qin has been looking for you.

00:32:54.480 --> 00:32:55.920
So you used me, Xiao Wuyi.

00:32:56.200 --> 00:32:59.060
You knew all along that Yuan Xiaoliu is Mulian Ying.

00:33:01.000 --> 00:33:01.790
Xiao Wuyi,

00:33:02.310 --> 00:33:03.920
When did you find out who I am?

00:33:04.350 --> 00:33:05.400
On the day I saved you,

00:33:05.400 --> 00:33:07.160
I knew you were from Northern Qin.

00:33:07.160 --> 00:33:09.480
It just didn't cross my mind that you're Mulian Ying.

00:33:09.480 --> 00:33:10.480
Over these years, the Northern Qin spies'

00:33:10.480 --> 00:33:11.880
Top priority in Jiankang

00:33:12.240 --> 00:33:13.720
Has always been finding Mulian Ying.

00:33:13.720 --> 00:33:17.050
The Empress Dowager of Northern Qin is in Jiankang right now

00:33:17.200 --> 00:33:18.860
As a member of the delegation.

00:33:20.240 --> 00:33:23.590
Mulian Ying and I were once in love.

00:33:24.510 --> 00:33:28.030
However, the palace lanterns burn long, casting light on the iron warrant.

00:33:28.030 --> 00:33:31.030
The bounds of the inner court are like a moat to heaven.

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:33.530
Despite all those great ambitions he had,

00:33:33.590 --> 00:33:36.190
The then emperor saw him as a potential hazard.

00:33:36.270 --> 00:33:38.720
I thought I could at least keep him alive.

00:33:39.400 --> 00:33:40.460
But unexpectedly,

00:33:41.920 --> 00:33:45.050
I ended up causing the destruction of his entirely clan.

00:33:47.480 --> 00:33:49.240
Being plagued by an old illness,

00:33:49.240 --> 00:33:50.700
My life is coming to an end.

00:33:51.680 --> 00:33:53.310
I hope you can find him for me,

00:33:53.670 --> 00:33:56.000
So I can see him one last time before I pass,

00:33:58.270 --> 00:34:00.200
And clear up all these old grievances.

00:34:00.200 --> 00:34:01.400
What did you just say?

00:34:02.000 --> 00:34:03.480
What did you mean by "her life is coming to an end"?

00:34:03.480 --> 00:34:04.400
If you are that worried,

00:34:04.400 --> 00:34:06.200
I will take you to see her directly.

00:34:06.200 --> 00:34:09.000
How do you know if she's after Yuan Xiaoliu's life?

00:34:09.920 --> 00:34:10.710
Xiao Wuyi,

00:34:12.150 --> 00:34:13.949
Are you doing this for yourself,

00:34:14.590 --> 00:34:15.630
Or for me?

00:34:17.280 --> 00:34:19.880
I can not only help Li Lejun regain her freedom,

00:34:20.320 --> 00:34:23.360
But also form an alliance

00:34:23.590 --> 00:34:27.389
Between Northern Qin and Southern Ye against the Eagle King's will,

00:34:27.750 --> 00:34:29.409
Thus preventing years of war.

00:34:31.110 --> 00:34:33.400
What do you think, Young Lord Xiao?

00:34:34.550 --> 00:34:35.190
Xiao Wuyi,

00:34:35.800 --> 00:34:37.630
You promised me you'd help Lejun.

00:34:37.630 --> 00:34:38.710
Now the Empress Dowager wants to see Yuan Xiaoliu.

00:34:38.710 --> 00:34:39.840
This is our only chance.

00:34:39.840 --> 00:34:41.770
No, I can't hand over Yuan Xiaoliu.

00:34:41.770 --> 00:34:43.370
This is a risk I will not take.

00:34:45.010 --> 00:34:46.340
I won't let her kill you,

00:34:47.230 --> 00:34:48.690
Nor will I let you kill her.

00:34:50.440 --> 00:34:52.150
Over these years, you've been hiding your identity

00:34:52.150 --> 00:34:53.670
And producing weapons in Beifu

00:34:53.670 --> 00:34:54.810
To fight Northern Qin.

00:34:54.810 --> 00:34:55.630
Isn't it because

00:34:55.630 --> 00:34:58.030
You're still holding hatred in your heart?

00:34:59.000 --> 00:35:00.150
Do you think she's asking to meet you

00:35:00.150 --> 00:35:02.150
Just to do some catching up with you?

00:35:06.180 --> 00:35:06.980
Take him away.

00:35:24.070 --> 00:35:25.270
Go back to your place.

00:35:27.030 --> 00:35:28.630
I will figure something out.

00:35:28.630 --> 00:35:30.490
Is everything up for negotiation

00:35:30.880 --> 00:35:32.740
For your so-called greater good?

00:35:33.510 --> 00:35:34.910
And after being weighed,

00:35:35.440 --> 00:35:37.360
Those who are hurt and sacrificed

00:35:37.360 --> 00:35:38.760
Will always be us, right?

00:35:41.400 --> 00:35:43.270
The marriages arranged

00:35:43.630 --> 00:35:45.030
For me, Lejun,

00:35:46.880 --> 00:35:48.540
Sister Yuanji, and my mother,

00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:51.500
Are about schemes and manipulation.

00:35:51.920 --> 00:35:53.580
Nobody cares about true love.

00:35:57.070 --> 00:35:58.470
If given another chance,

00:35:59.070 --> 00:36:00.190
You would still marry Ms. He

00:36:00.190 --> 00:36:01.650
For military provisions,

00:36:01.880 --> 00:36:03.190
Ask the Empress Dowager to grant a marriage

00:36:03.190 --> 00:36:04.960
So as to pressure Prince Changsha,

00:36:04.960 --> 00:36:05.760
And still place Lejun

00:36:05.760 --> 00:36:07.880
At the very end of all considerations.

00:36:07.880 --> 00:36:09.280
This is what you're like,

00:36:10.510 --> 00:36:11.480
Xiao Wuyi.

00:36:18.110 --> 00:36:18.920
Not just you,

00:36:20.510 --> 00:36:21.640
Mao has changed too.

00:36:22.760 --> 00:36:25.110
He already started selecting concubines for himself.

00:36:25.110 --> 00:36:26.370
He has decided to stay,

00:36:27.800 --> 00:36:29.000
Yet he hasn't told me.

00:36:30.760 --> 00:36:31.890
I'm well aware of it,

00:36:32.400 --> 00:36:33.600
But I'm still arguing

00:36:34.230 --> 00:36:36.890
Relentlessly with you about Lejun's marriage.

00:36:37.070 --> 00:36:39.270
You must be laughing at me in your heart.

00:36:42.920 --> 00:36:43.720
You are right.

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:46.280
If given another chance,

00:36:48.400 --> 00:36:50.400
I would still make the same choices.

00:36:53.060 --> 00:36:54.660
But I will never laugh at you.

00:37:01.840 --> 00:37:02.840
I am sick and tired

00:37:04.280 --> 00:37:05.480
Of all that weighing.

00:37:07.400 --> 00:37:08.510
I will not give up.

00:37:09.360 --> 00:37:12.110
I will not let Lejun end up like me.

00:37:29.920 --> 00:37:33.230
Princess Pingning shall enter the hall.

00:37:43.450 --> 00:37:48.020
♪ If fate is fragile, what is right or wrong ♪

00:37:49.910 --> 00:37:54.910
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

00:37:55.350 --> 00:37:58.970
♪ Love and hate fade like the shifting sand ♪

00:37:58.990 --> 00:38:01.930
♪ What's right or wrong is better left unsaid ♪

00:38:01.950 --> 00:38:07.670
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

00:38:08.300 --> 00:38:11.690
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

00:38:11.710 --> 00:38:14.730
♪ The heart's a cage, but peace will break the chains ♪

00:38:14.750 --> 00:38:20.500
♪ No need to speak, just leave it all to fate ♪

00:38:33.840 --> 00:38:37.330
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

00:38:37.350 --> 00:38:40.300
♪ The heart's a cage, but peace will break the chains ♪

00:38:40.320 --> 00:38:47.160
♪ No need to speak, just leave it all to fate ♪

00:38:52.840 --> 00:38:55.030
I, Li Lejun, Princess Pingning, extend

00:38:55.030 --> 00:38:56.690
My greetings to Your Majesty.

00:38:56.710 --> 00:38:57.800
Long live

00:38:58.550 --> 00:38:59.710
Your Majesties.

00:39:22.070 --> 00:39:22.840
Your Highness?

00:39:22.840 --> 00:39:24.170
Yuan Xiaoliu, come out!

00:39:24.280 --> 00:39:26.040
Yuan Xiaoliu is not in this carriage.

00:39:26.040 --> 00:39:27.970
He already boarded a ship and left.

00:39:30.880 --> 00:39:33.440
Yuan Xiaoliu, I know you are inside, and that you're still

00:39:33.440 --> 00:39:35.960
Still thinking about the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin.

00:39:35.960 --> 00:39:37.350
Her heart disease is incurable,

00:39:37.350 --> 00:39:38.810
And her days are numbered.

00:39:39.110 --> 00:39:40.040
If you leave now,

00:39:40.280 --> 00:39:42.960
You might never get to see her again in the rest of your life.

00:39:42.960 --> 00:39:44.630
Listen up. Tonight,

00:39:44.630 --> 00:39:45.800
I've arranged a Northern Qin puppet show

00:39:45.800 --> 00:39:47.000
In Xiyue Restaurant.

00:39:47.320 --> 00:39:49.180
It is up to you whether to go or not.

00:39:49.680 --> 00:39:52.410
You'd hate to have regrets for a lifetime, right?

00:40:00.400 --> 00:40:01.200
Yuan Xiaoliu.

00:40:01.390 --> 00:40:03.180
Mr. Yuan, do not act rashly.

00:40:03.550 --> 00:40:04.840
It's His Highness's order

00:40:04.840 --> 00:40:06.240
That you will be executed

00:40:06.550 --> 00:40:08.480
On the spot if you defy the command.

00:40:13.710 --> 00:40:16.230
All the 138 members of the Yuan clan

00:40:17.630 --> 00:40:19.160
Died because of that woman.

00:40:19.960 --> 00:40:21.760
I severed ties with her long ago.

00:40:22.150 --> 00:40:24.840
Now, hearing that she is about to die,

00:40:25.800 --> 00:40:29.460
I only feel the pleasure of having my greatest revenge fulfilled.

00:40:30.550 --> 00:40:31.920
I will never

00:40:32.510 --> 00:40:33.320
See her again.

00:40:33.840 --> 00:40:34.480
Qing Long,

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:36.150
Let's go.

00:40:49.590 --> 00:40:50.520
You really came.

00:40:50.920 --> 00:40:52.510
If Xiao Wuyi finds out about this,

00:40:52.510 --> 00:40:52.920
I will...

00:40:52.920 --> 00:40:53.650
Don't worry.

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:56.400
I promise to save your life with mine today.

00:40:56.440 --> 00:40:57.440
If the Empress Dowager of Northern Qin

00:40:57.440 --> 00:40:58.970
Truly attempts to hurt you,

00:40:59.320 --> 00:41:00.440
I will shield you

00:41:00.510 --> 00:41:01.640
And let you go first.

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:03.550
You have my word.

00:41:05.440 --> 00:41:07.630
Xiao Wuyi will be furious then.

00:41:08.440 --> 00:41:09.370
What did you say?

00:41:09.780 --> 00:41:10.510
Nothing.

00:41:11.080 --> 00:41:11.840
I mean,

00:41:12.030 --> 00:41:13.150
Are you really planning

00:41:13.150 --> 00:41:14.800
To risk your life for the cancellation

00:41:14.800 --> 00:41:16.130
Of Li Lejun's marriage?

00:41:16.760 --> 00:41:17.670
Isn't this

00:41:17.760 --> 00:41:19.490
What friends do for each other?

00:41:20.510 --> 00:41:22.030
Moved by your chivalry,

00:41:22.360 --> 00:41:25.490
I've decided to stand or fall together with you tonight.

00:41:35.030 --> 00:41:37.030
Today is your wedding day.

00:41:38.110 --> 00:41:40.110
Prince Qi claimed to be sick and took leave from court.

00:41:40.110 --> 00:41:42.310
Young Lord Xiao hasn't shown up either.

00:41:42.480 --> 00:41:43.630
Could it be that the two of them

00:41:43.630 --> 00:41:45.580
Are dissatisfied with this marriage

00:41:45.580 --> 00:41:48.110
And are working together to object it for you?

00:41:54.190 --> 00:41:55.450
It doesn't matter now.

00:42:01.800 --> 00:42:03.030
The auspicious hour has arrived.

00:42:03.030 --> 00:42:04.400
His Highness the Eagle King

00:42:04.400 --> 00:42:07.660
And Princess Pingning shall perform the bowing ceremony.

00:42:12.230 --> 00:42:14.000
Eagle King, please bow.

00:42:16.960 --> 00:42:18.760
Princess Pingning, please bow.

00:42:24.960 --> 00:42:27.000
Princess Pingning, please bow.

